    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready for a great deal on a car with plenty of life left! This vehicle is in fair condition and shows some honest wear from its time on the road, but it remains a dependable choice for anyone looking for affordable transportation. It's a functional, straightforward ride that\u2019s perfect for a daily commuter or someone looking for a solid value!",
