    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this distinguished vehicle, a testament to disciplined maintenance and enduring mechanical integrity. This specimen offers a refined driving experience, characterized by consistent performance and a well-preserved aesthetic. Having undergone a comprehensive professional assessment, the vehicle stands as a premier choice for those seeking reliability without compromise. Its sophisticated profile and robust operational history ensure it meets the rigorous demands of daily use while maintaining a commanding presence on the road.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 18
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my trusty car. It\u2019s been such a reliable ride for me and is still in really solid shape, perfect for someone who wants a dependable vehicle without the brand-new price tag. It runs smoothly and has been well-cared for, so it\u2019s ready to hit the road with you today! Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I\u2019d love to tell you more about it!",
      "price": 28900.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 18
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Up for sale is a mechanically robust E46 M3 powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six. This engine features individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system that has been recently recalibrated for peak torque delivery. The 6-speed Getrag manual transmission shifts with precision, sending power through a factory M-Variable differential lock. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including rear subframe reinforcement and rod bearing inspection. The chassis remains taut with upgraded polyurethane bushings and refreshed dampers, ensuring the linear steering response and turn-in characteristics this platform is known for. A true driver\u2019s car with sorted internals.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 18
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used vehicle. Good condition. Reliable daily driver. Clean title. Routine maintenance performed. Minor surface scratches. Firm price.",
      "price": 28900.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 18
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a well-maintained example of its model, offering a perfect balance of reliability and aesthetic appeal. The exterior paint retains a deep, lustrous shine, though a careful walk-around will reveal a few minor stone chips on the front fascia and a small, superficial scratch near the rear wheel well\u2014typical signs of careful road use. The body panels are straight with consistent gaps throughout. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary of comfort; the leather upholstery is supple and free of tears, showing only light, natural creasing on the driver\u2019s seat bolster. All interior electronics, including the premium sound system and navigation, are fully operational. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly with no unusual noises, backed by a comprehensive service history that includes recent fluid changes and a cooling system flush. The transmission shifts seamlessly through all gears. With approximately 70% tread remaining on the tires and firm, responsive brakes, this car is mechanically sound and ready for the road. It has been kept in a smoke-free environment and professionally detailed for the new owner.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
